						<dl>
							<dd><i>For how to handle having multiple region maps, see <a href="/web/20210603015015/https://essentialsdocs.fandom.com/wiki/Multiple_regions" title="Multiple regions">Multiple regions</a>.</i></dd>
							<dd><i>For linking a game map to a particular spot on the region map, see <a href="/web/20210603015015/https://essentialsdocs.fandom.com/wiki/Maps" title="Maps">Maps</a>.</i></dd>
